metadata.name: DragonEye 1:1
metadata.description: The DragonEye is the first ever, one of one, patented, asset-backed, self-liquidating NFT. It is tied to a 27.5 carat authenticated and certified Brazilian Paraiba. At maturity, the NFT will be burned and the owner will take possession of the physical asset. For more information visit www.findtheforbidden.com.
